<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Bug posted by Vladas Diržys on public mailing list.</p>

<p>{quote}
I think there is an error in documentation.</p>

<p><a href="http://framework.zend.com/manual/en/zend.http.cookies.html">http://framework.zend.com/manual/en/…</a></p>

<p>Example 17.22. and forward uses:
$cookie = Zend_Http_Client('foo=two+words; ....);</p>

<p>but it should be:
$cookie = Zend_Http_Cookie('foo=two+words; ....);
{quote}</p>

